problem_statement:
Java idempotency issue with `instanceof final` pattern matching
## What version of OpenRewrite are you using?

Current main = 45ca3c98d074f7434f8d4aec781228619b21313d

## What is the smallest, simplest way to reproduce the problem?

```java
    @Test
    void instanceofFinal() {
        rewriteRun(
          java(
            """
            public class Main {
              public static void main(String[] argv) {
                String s = "a";
                if (s instanceof final String s2) {
                    System.out.println(s2);
                }
              }
            }
            """
          )
        );
    }
```

## What did you expect to see?

No change.

## What did you see instead?

```diff
-       if (s instanceof final String s2) {
+       if (s instanceof StringString s2) {
```

