problem_statement:
RenameVariable does not modify variables referenced through type casts
## What version of OpenRewrite are you using?

I am using

- OpenRewrite v8.17.1
- Maven/Gradle plugin v6.8.4
- rewrite-java v8.17.1

## What is the smallest, simplest way to reproduce the problem?

### Before

```java
package demo;
	
import java.util.Arrays;

public class BugDemo {
 
  private final Object[] objArray;

  public BugDemo(Object... objects) {
	this.objArray = objects;
  }

  public boolean isEqualTo(Object object) {
	return Arrays.equals(objArray, ((BugDemo) object).objArray);
  }

  public int length() {
	return objArray.length;
  }
} 
```

I run

```java
@NonNull
