problem_statement:
NameCaseConvention.LOWER_CAMEL should handle mixed case more properly
Actual:

```diff
-      PdfDocumentViewModel PDFviewModel = new PdfDocumentViewModel(mockPDF);
+      PdfDocumentViewModel pDFviewModel = new PdfDocumentViewModel(mockPDF);
```

Expected

```diff
-      PdfDocumentViewModel PDFviewModel = new PdfDocumentViewModel(mockPDF);
+      PdfDocumentViewModel pdfViewModel = new PdfDocumentViewModel(mockPdf);
